v0.27  2025-12-18Z
    - Updated documentation
    - Accept negative numbers for RoarAudio error numbers
    - Added uuidhexdash, and uuidHEXDASH packing formats
    - Improved experimental skip_invalid support

v0.26  2025-11-25Z
    - Updated documentation
    - Added experimental Data::Identifier::Wellknown->announce()
    - Added experimental style => 'uriid' to $identifier->uri()
    - Improved SIRTX identifier parsing

v0.25  2025-11-19Z
    - Added new SID values
    - Added support for wd:TNNN parsing and rendering in Util
    - Fix Unicode character generator to correctly emit displaynames
    - Added basic language generator

v0.24  2025-11-10Z
    - Added support for Data::Identifier::Util->render_sirtx()
    - Fixed parsing of SIRTX identifiers
    - Include generator for generated well known tags
    - Added new SID values

v0.23  2025-11-03Z
    - Added Data::Identifier::Util

v0.22  2025-10-29Z
    - Support Data::TagMap as tagmap in Data::Identifier::Interface::Subobjects
    - Support SIRTX::Datecode as $as in as()
    - Support converting from SIRTX::Datecode in new() via from
    - Support converting from Data::Identifier::Interface::Simple in new() via from

v0.21  2025-10-26Z
    - Updated list of well known languages
    - Updated list of well known tags related to character sets

v0.20  2025-10-20Z
    - Fixed $identifier->as($type) if $identifiers->type->eq($type) is true

v0.19  2025-10-19Z
    - Added basic support for host defined identifiers and user defined identifiers
    - Added new SID and SNI values
    - Added support for $identifier->as() to take a Data::Identifier as 'as'

